+# Phase 15A — Practical User Test Case Suite
+
+## Purpose
+Create a hands-on user test suite that finds real workflow issues, UX friction, authorization gaps, deployment problems, and data consistency issues in currently implemented CadreOS behavior.
+
+## Scope Guardrails (Do Not Expand)
+- No new product/runtime features.
+- No messaging, notifications, Feed, Inbox, Journal, AI, automation, offline sync, or native mobile behavior.
+- No FieldOps or Entry runtime feature expansion.
+- Focus only on test planning, validation scenarios, and issue discovery for existing flows.
+
+## Confirmed Current Workflow Coverage Baseline
+This suite is aligned to implemented routes/models in current CadreOS:
+- Auth/bootstrap/linking: `/sign-in`, `/account/link-person`, `/account/bootstrap-admin`
+- Org/program/team/person model: Organization, Program, Team, Season, Person
+- Roles/roster/guardian visibility: RoleAssignment, RosterMembership, AthleteGuardianRelationship, staff-scoped guardian diagnostics
+- Events/attendance: Event + AttendanceRecord capture/update flows
+- Notes/tasks: ObservationNote + FollowUpTask create/review/edit flows
+- Dashboard/review: dashboard review cards + operational panels
+- FieldOps MVP: facilities/resources/bookings and approval/precheck workflows
+- Entry wrapper/context: `EntryRuntimeRef` + `/entry-runtime/[entryRuntimeRefId]` read-only relationship view
+- Rapid-capture/mobile web optimization: dashboard rapid actions, context prefill, return-path continuity, attendance continue-capture
+
+## Shared Test Data Preconditions
+Use seeded/demo baseline (or equivalent) before executing persona cases:
+- Demo organization, program, team, season exist.
+- At least one person for each role type: Org Admin, Program Director, Coach, Assistant Coach, Athlete, Parent/Guardian.
+- Team has at least one ATHLETE roster member and one staff member.
+- At least one athlete has guardian relationship; at least one athlete intentionally missing guardian relationship for edge tests.
+- At least one event exists for team and one event without team.
+- At least one ObservationNote and one FollowUpTask exist.
+- At least one FieldOps facility/resource pair exists.
+- Account-linking users available for staff and non-staff personas.
+
+## Testing Status Tracker
+Use this status in every test execution row:
+- **NOT TESTED**
+- **PASS**
+- **FAIL**
+- **BLOCKED**
+- **NEEDS RETEST**
+
