+---
+
+## Validation Notes for Phase 15A
+- Test cases are mapped to currently implemented models/routes and avoid deferred scope.
+- No assumptions are made about messaging/notifications/feed/inbox/journal/AI/automation/offline/native mobile behavior.
+- Guardian/parent flows are treated as visibility/context-only where currently supported.
+- FieldOps and Entry runtime are validated as implemented (MVP/read-only metadata) without runtime expansion.
+
+## PR Summary (Coverage + Known Gaps)
+This Phase 15A suite adds a persona-organized manual validation matrix across auth/bootstrap, org/program/team/person structure, role/roster workflows, guardian visibility diagnostics, events/attendance, notes/tasks, dashboard/review workflows, FieldOps MVP, Entry relationship wrapper behavior, rapid-capture mobile-web usability, and deployment smoke verification. It includes required end-to-end paths, explicit negative/edge cases, a defect template, and a status tracker for execution governance.
+
+Known gaps intentionally preserved in this phase:
+- No new runtime features were added.
+- Deferred capabilities remain deferred (messaging, notifications, Feed/Inbox/Journal runtime, AI/recommendation/automation, offline sync, native mobile behavior).
+- Guardian runtime workflows remain visibility/context-oriented and staff-scoped where currently implemented.
